We're at Asahikawa.

50
00:02:25,045 --> 00:02:27,948
-Nice to meet you.
-Nice to meet you.

51
00:02:28,015 --> 00:02:29,716
I'm Sung Si-kyung.

52
00:02:29,783 --> 00:02:32,753
-I know.
-Thank you.

53
00:02:33,520 --> 00:02:36,023
Aren't you from Kushiro,
in eastern Hokkaido?

54
00:02:36,089 --> 00:02:37,257
Yes, that's right.

55
00:02:37,324 --> 00:02:39,126
Then when did you move to Asahikawa?

56
00:02:39,192 --> 00:02:40,694
When I was 18.

57
00:02:41,395 --> 00:02:43,730
-It's been almost 30 years now.
-I see.

58
00:02:43,797 --> 00:02:47,934
Anyway, I don't think there's anyone
who can draw food illustrations

59
00:02:48,368 --> 00:02:50,470
