want to say it too.

70
00:03:16,263 --> 00:03:17,764
It's an obanzai restaurant.

71
00:03:17,831 --> 00:03:24,438
I believe the word obanzai
originally comes from Kyoto,

72
00:03:24,504 --> 00:03:28,909
referring to everyday home cooking.

73
00:03:28,975 --> 00:03:31,912
In other words, the taste of home.

74
00:03:31,978 --> 00:03:33,447
I love it.

75
